snippet.title: Cat TV for Cats to Watch
snippet.description:
Cat TV that will leave your cat utterly spellbound as they witness the non-stop, mesmerising parade of delightful birds and mischievous squirrels gracing our garden with their enchanting presence!

Regular Visitors:
Grey Squirrel
Woodpigeon
Robin
Blackbird
Starling
Coal Tit
Blue Tit
Magpie
Jackdaw
Collared Dove
Carrion Crow

Occasional Visitors:
Nuthatch
Dunnock
Greater Spotted Woodpecker

Rare Visitors:
Blackhat
Wren
Goldcrest


👍 Like, Super Thanks, Subscribe. All support is welcome. 👍

All video and audio recorded in Patsy's Garden (not always at the same time). 

Do not copy, reproduce, or distribute any of the content. This includes running our thumbnails through AI.

#cattv #videosforcats #dogtv #videosfordogs #birdsforcatstowatch #birding #birder #birders #noads

— 

When not in our garden we enjoy walking our two dogs in nearby ancient woodland and coastal paths. We occasionally film these walks to create calming videos for dogs and their owners to relax to and enjoy.
